{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a13e32a490","title":"给萧军的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7422ec1855","index":0,"year":1941,"month":8,"day":2,"articleId":"a13e32a490","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"书信","id":"2a70b5d939","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji2","name":"毛泽东文集第二卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"/books/wenji2.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji2":{"comments":[{"id":"72cefab2ae","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"a13e32a490","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":3,"text":"萧军（一九○七——一九八八），辽宁锦县人。当时任中华全国文艺界抗敌协会延安分会理事。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8262800de2","type":"title","text":"给萧军的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"a13e32a490","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"72cefab2ae","type":"appellation","text":"萧军同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"a13e32a490","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6f990dba50","type":"paragraph","text":"两次来示都阅悉，要的书已付上。我因过去同你少接触，缺乏了解，有些意见想同你说，又怕交浅言深，无益于你，反引起隔阂，故没有即说。延安有无数的坏现象，你对我说的，都值得注意，都应改正。但我劝你同时注意自己方面的某些毛病，不要绝对地看问题，要有耐心，要注意调理人我关系，要故意地强制地省察自己的弱点，方有出路，方能“安心立命”。否则天天不安心，痛苦甚大。你是极坦白豪爽的人，我觉得我同你谈得来，故提议如上。如得你同意，愿同你再谈一回。敬问近好！","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"a13e32a490","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3ec4fce71f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"a13e32a490","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a04a09875","type":"paragraph","text":"八月二日","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"a13e32a490","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"66c641e244","type":"paragraph","text":"根据人民出版社一九八三年出版的","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"a13e32a490","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bfb426a010","type":"paragraph","text":"《毛泽东书信选集》刊印。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"a13e32a490","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":377,"end":377}}}},"__N_SSG":true}